Codex Autoresearch Convo
NOTICE

This repository is a derivative work based on:

  leo-lilinxiao/codex-autoresearch
  https://github.com/leo-lilinxiao/codex-autoresearch

The Convo variant preserves the upstream autonomous loop core while adding
research-oriented workflow changes, including:

- conversational first-run onboarding
- canonical repo-local research memory
- delta-only returning runs
- multi-guard runtime metadata
- richer research reporting
- legacy-to-canonical research schema migration helpers
- Windows-focused installation and encoding guidance

